title: Tomb of Patra
story: Patra is long gone, but people are still reluctant to come close to the tomb. Recently an undead spectral wasp has made its lair here. Word is that countless treasures of ancient books can be found here.

notes.text: A large wooden door with two keyholes to the north.
A stuffed dwarf with a mysterious, warm to touch tiara in their hands.
Remains of a gnome, some gold and a potion of invisibility clutched in his hands.
A scarf hidden in a crack of the wall.
A rear entrance into the tomb. A mosaic of a bat pattern on the walls
An impossible puzzle, transforms a person into a gnoll when solved.
A rotten crate with an iron key in it.
A chest containing an iron key.
